casebody.data:
MAKAH INDIAN TRIBE, petitioner,
v.
QUILEUTE INDIAN TRIBE, et al. No. 17-1592. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 1, 2018.

Motion of United Catcher Boats for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
